  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Brush pirozhki dough with sesame oil and bake for 10-12 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "In a pan, cook ground beef over medium-high heat until browned, breaking into small pieces as it cooks.",
    "Add fermented Thai chili sauce and stir to combine.",
    "Add green onions and stir-fry until wilted.",
    "Spoon a small amount of the beef mixture onto each pirozhki.",
    "Top with a dollop of apricot jam and a sprinkle of crispy fried shallots.",
